title: iDevice Manager Pro-Edition 8.4.0.0 Full + Medicine[BabuPC]
description:
[img]http://babupc.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/iDevice-Manager-Pro-Edition.gif[/img]

iDevice Manager Pro Edition

Use iDevice Manager (former iPhone Explorer) to transfer music, photos, videos, address book contacts, notes, calendar items, SMS WhatsApp messages and many other files to copy from iPhone and iPad to your Windows computer! Together with our free iManager app is it also possible to transfer contacts, pictures and videos to the popular Apple iPhone! The iDevice Manager contains a function to create backups of your Apple devices without iTunes. The program is free to use, but it has usage restrictions in this version. Discover today the functions and download the program on your PC. Of course, the program is free of ads, adware, viruses and other bad software. Your virus scanner will prove it.

The iDevice Manager Pro-Edition is an extension of the free iDevice Manager to backup of iPhone and iPad files on your Windows computer and to create new unlimited ringtones from MP3 files. Together with the free iManager App is it possible to upload address book contacts, photos and videos to the iPad and iPhone.
Supported Devices:

    Apple iOS 11, 10, 9, 8, 7 firmware devices
    iPad Pro, iPad Air 2, iPad Air, iPad 4
    iPad mini
    iPhone X, iPhone 8 Plus, 8, iPhone 7 Plus, 7, 6S Plus, 6S, 6 Plus, 6, 5S, 5C, 5
